                    // biome-palette base. Kills the "three concentric
                    // flat-colour rings at the pole" look that discrete
                    // ice/alpine biomes produced, and gives mountains
                    // shaded relief at orbital distance.
                    PaintBiomes((
                        ocean_depth: Some((
                            // Muted shelf teal — Apollo-era Bahamas /
                            // Caribbean shallows. Linear (0.04, 0.11,
                            // 0.16) ≈ sRGB (56, 96, 116): a dim teal
